parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front leaf springs can cause the vehicle to sag, leading to uneven tire wear, reduced handling, and increased risk of accidents. In severe cases, it can cause damage to the fender and surrounding components.
symptoms: The front of the vehicle sags
the front tires wear unevenly
the front fender is damaged
the vehicle is difficult to handle
the vehicle is hazardous to drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The separation of the windshield from the frame can cause water leaks, reduced visibility, and increased risk of accidents. In severe cases, it can lead to the windshield breaking, causing further damage and safety risks.
symptoms: The windshield starts to separate from the frame
water leaks into the vehicle
visibility is reduced
the windshield breaks when leveling the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Engagement of Electro-Hydraulic Driveline Mounted Parking Brake/Autopark System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended engagement of the parking brake/autopark system can cause the vehicle to suddenly stop or lose control, leading to accidents or injuries. The failure of the parking brake and park position on the transmission can also lead to rollaway accidents when parking.
symptoms: The parking brake/autopark system engages on its own while driving
the vehicle suddenly stops or locks up
the parking brake/autopark system fails to release
the fuse blows repeatedly
the parking brake and park position on the transmission become inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water accumulation in the basement compartments can cause corrosion, electrical issues, and damage to components, potentially leading to safety hazards and costly repairs.
symptoms: Water accumulation in the basement compartments
water damage to components
corrosion
electrical issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The absence of a second gas strut can cause the door to fall or drop suddenly, potentially causing injury or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Door falls or drops suddenly
difficulty opening or closing the door
uneven door alignment.
